title: The Power of Momentum
itunes:title: The Power of Momentum
description:
If you are working on growing yourself or your business, you will eventually get momentum on your side. Momentum can either take your life to an amazing level or if not harnessed correctly, make you crash. In this episode, I will teach you how to harness the power of momentum!
